com.ic.invisiblecollector.model

Enum CompanyField

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<CompanyField>
      • com.ic.invisiblecollector.model.CompanyField
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ICheckableField, java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<CompanyField>

    public enum CompanyField
extends java.lang.Enum<CompanyField>
implements ICheckableField
    The attributes which can be used to update a company's information in the database.

    Intended to be used in conjunction with an enum map.

    See also Company for a ready 'container' of these attributes.

    Author:
    ros
